snippet.title: Evercade - Duke Nukem Collections 1 & 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Evercade and Gearbox present six great games from the Duke Nukem franchise, available on two physical cartridge collections. And introducing Duke Nukem 1+2 Remastered - developed by Blaze Entertainment!

November 2023
Pre-order August 2023

https://evercade.co.uk/dukenukem

Full Games List
Duke Nukem Collection 1 - Duke Nukem 1+2 Remastered, Duke Nukem 3D

Duke Nukem Collection 2 - Duke Nukem Time to Kill, Duke Nukem Land of the Babes, Duke Nukem Advance

Website: evercade.co.uk
